The paper deals with image processing and specifically with saliency detection, which is a common task in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes the use of convolutional neural networks, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with image manipulation (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it aims to identify the most important parts of an image.
